    "attributes": {
        "action": "Pay a one off sum of \u00a35,000 to every events company in the UK",
        "additional_details": "We want the government to do this to ensure the survival of the events industry , to ensure that when we do come back we will be back , to help these small / medium business to see there is light at the end of the tunnel before we go bankrupt and to show that the government cares about this sector and it isn\u2019t just being brushed under the carpet , every grant so far has been unsuitable for most in our industry it\u2019s time you help us",
        "background": "Events businesses have suffered great loss due to the COVID 19 pandemic but have still had to continue paying out for rent & equipment insurance to name a few ,we get we will we allowed back the question is will we still be here? We want you to support us without a stringent criteria for applicants",
